Take the packet of Maggi
Start to cut the packet and break the solid noodles into small and long noodles
Now put some water and the maggi along with a packet of masala in a bowl
Put the bowl inside the microven and set 2 minute time
After that your maggi is ready.

Link of making KFC chicken is given below: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nqwvvmzfWDA
